      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALFIE'S POP (7) was a last start winner (23.29) at this track who is building a strong winning record. Is yet to taste defeat at this distance. In sparkling form and looks the one to beat again. SWIPER LANE (2) has been hard to follow lately, running fifth (20.25) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Can improve sharply here. HECTIC BLUE (1) turned in a plain run last time when sixth at Maitland over 400m behind Mighty Henry (23.19) in a Grade 5. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to her credit. A big run wouldn't surprise. MY OCTAVIUS (8) is very honest and looms as a strong top-three hope again.",
